f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"TAXI pls"},{"pid":"e896477817ae66146ad2641bf387278be050da3d","tid":1112093,"uid":192052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3998480ddcc7272f70a68d4e453892d3c8134e64","tid":1112093,"uid":62192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"無黃紙你話考左500次都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:58:17.000Z","msg":"有幾多人會吹自己考五次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔夠樣衰咩"},{"pid":"75e5b1c824c14b1dd23c6d01462b164304011d1d","tid":1112093,"uid":240879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:33:09.000Z","msg":"無謂害人害己"},{"pid":"38dd840d2b2d9791b99e866a3121c5bab68bb2a8","tid":1112093,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"求下你<br />\n為己為人唔好揸車"},{"pid":"cd08c0d7172fcf2df6ecad2c7fc794cf5d658a4e","tid":1112093,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"唔該俾啲自知之明<br />\n<br />\n1take pass唔到嘅<br />\n<br />\n唔該搭車啦<br />\n<br />\n咪撚出嚟害人<br />\n<br />\n條街已經好多車"},{"pid":"1c700257140f81c8219bca4ef5ca8328715346f0","tid":1112093,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b75f68a22dc39da390b35dc3bf637ae45bc58389","tid":1112093,"uid":243635,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"駄盤控制不當係咪你轉完灣, 鬆手自動回駄啊?<br />\n利申:鬆手自動回駄撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"鬆手自動回軚係冇問題<br />\n<br />\n鬆一隻，另一隻扮回咁搭落下一格係work嘅"},{"pid":"29638354c8824356cc3b2cec3b58da06bbecdd9a","tid":1112093,"uid":161815,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T22:32:42.000Z","msg":"親愛的樓主:<br />\n<br />\n大家都是熱愛生命的人，請你放低主見，接受大家的建議。考車個幾千蚊，你當發咗場夢又好，比咗人去賭哂都好，主動放棄考車，發誓以後坐的士，或者叫親朋戚友車你喇。<br />\n祝願一生平安<br />\n<br />\n一羣熱愛生命的人上"},{"pid":"127b0659561ff40db0ed7841809815ac3bc66b30","tid":1112093,"uid":205844,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T22:49:46.000Z","msg":"德國：最多只可考5次<br />\n<br />\n在德國考車牌絕不容易，先要上14堂理論課和12堂駕駛課，包括高速公路、公路以及夜路駕駛，大部分駕駛細節都無一倖免，監考非常嚴格。考生只一生只有五次機會，如果到了第三次都無法成功，就會被送去參與智商和判斷力的測試，如果仍然未能通過，表示你是「不適合開車的人」。<br />\n此外，在德國考車牌除了先要通過視力測試，外加完成8小時的急救課程，學習人工呼吸、心肺復蘇、止血等簡單的急救知識，以便日後遇上交通意外，都可自救，而駕駛者亦有責任對受傷的人施行急救。<br />\n<br />\n樓豬去驗下智商先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03943efec98fa2df85e082374b12f82210ccf6d","tid":1112093,"uid":248495,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"f98e16a6e82be0fe5079e329a1bdada2a20f5a70","tid":1112093,"uid":222107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:41:02.000Z","msg":"好灰...今日考私家車自動波考第五次都未pass..前幾次衰騰雞我認，今次考完我仲以為自己實得，但又剔我駄盤控制不當..我今次真係唔知自己衰乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想問報駕駛學院係咪會易pass啲嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"當然唔係。駕駛學院學車路線就係考牌路線，所以考官可能會更加嚴格。<br />\n利申：報駕駛學院，第四次先pass"},{"pid":"ee0c6b9a9050639e6f0d7be8c2b8114e2b472e4e","tid":1112093,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1c700257140f81c8219bca4ef5ca8328715346f0","tid":1112093,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b75f68a22dc39da390b35dc3bf637ae45bc58389","tid":1112093,"uid":243635,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"cit